This paper is primarily focused on intrusion detection in IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques such as self-learning and federated learning, which are commonly used in the fields of networking and artificial intelligence (cs.NI and cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of distributed systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper extensively evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed system, which could fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
